BirthData.DetailedNotes: Educational psychologist. Controversial theory relating race to intelligence. Most villified figure in psychology, physically threatened, burned in effigy. Book set off bitter controversity, still continued his research. Almost somber figure, aloof, dignified, mild mannered. Dark attire, honest, cloistered life style, dedicated to work. Lonely, humorously absent minded, a professor's professor. CB 73. .
